==States form==

This is the application of states, with it you can add, modify and view all data from the states ranked in different tabs: main data, application permissions, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===State Data Tab===

In this tab you can view and modify the main state data. Here we relate all information fields.

[estados-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** State name.
- **Application (*):** Application that is linked state.
- **Position (*):** Status position compared to other states linked with your application.
- **Active:** If the state can be used in the linked application.
- **Description:** Description of the state in which cases are used, etc ...


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a state Campos.**

